
"In episode 2 of Open Up! Podcast, we interview Steve Carson–Evaluation Coordinator and Senior Strategist for MIT’s OpenCourseWare project.

In this interview, Steven discusses:

* A bit about his own background and experience leading up to his joining the MIT OCW team
    
* The origins of MIT OpenCourseWare
    
* MIT OCW’s evolution to its current state of over 1,250 published courses
    
* A brief status of the OpenCourseWare movement worldwide
    
* The future of MIT OCW"

